ustria]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web| title=Bundeskanzler Anfragebeantwortung An die Pr\u00e4sidentin des Nationalrats| url=http://www.parlament.gv.at/PAKT/VHG/XXIV/AB/AB_10542/imfname_251156.pdf|trans-title=Reply to a parliamentary question about the Decoration of Honour| language=German|website=Parlament.gv.at| page=168| accessdate=1 November 2012}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Bahrain}}: Collar of the [http://medals.org.uk/bahrain/bahrain001.htm Order of Khalifa]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://a.bt.bmcdn.dk/media/cache/resolve/image_1260x840/image/16/165435/3828674-margrethe.jpg|format=JKPG|title=King Hamad hands the insignia to Queen Margrethe in exchange of the Order of the Dannebrog|website=A.bt.bmcdn.dk|accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Belgium}}: Grand Cordon of the [[Order of Leopold (Belgium)|Order of Leopold]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://1.t.cdn.belga.be/picture:954544:preview:watermark |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425130022/http://1.t.cdn.belga.be/picture%3A954544%3Apreview%3Awatermark |url-status=dead |archive-date=25 April 2012 |title=Photographic image |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Brazil}}: Grand Collar of the [[Order of the Southern Cross]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Bulgaria}}: Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Stara Planina]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gettyimages.co.uk/detail/news-photo/president-of-bulgaria-georgi-parvanov-and-danish-queen-news-photo/57207879|title=Georgi Parvanov|author=KELD NAVNTOFT|work=Getty Images|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://c7.alamy.com/comp/FHC0JE/epa00680421-president-of-the-republic-of-bulgaria-georgi-parvanov-FHC0JE.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=C7.alamy.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Chile}}: Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Merit of Chile]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Croa