rums.com/forums/f68/queen-margrethe-and-prince-henriks-state-visit-to-japan-november-15-22-2004-a-4081.html|title=Queen Margrethe and Prince Henrik's State Visit to Japan: November 15-22, 2004 - The Royal Forums|website=Theroyalforums.com|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gettyimages.ca/detail/news-photo/queen-margrethe-ii-prince-henrik-of-denmarks-state-visit-to-news-photo/157801758|title=Empress Michiko|author=Julian Parker|work=Getty Images|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Japan}}: Grand Cordon (Paulownia) of the [[Order of the Precious Crown]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Jordan}}: Grand Cordon with Collar of the [[Order of al-Hussein bin Ali]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Latvia}}: Commander Grand Cross with Chain of the [[Order of the Three Stars]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Lithuania}}: Grand Cross of the [[Order of Vytautas the Great]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref name=Lithuania>{{cite web|title=Apdovanojimai |trans-title=Awards Database |url=http://www.lrp.lt/lt/prezidento_veikla/apdovanojimai/apdovanojimai_256/p40.html |publisher=President of the Republic of Lithuania |accessdate=11 December 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419212238/http://www.lrp.lt/lt/prezidento_veikla/apdovanojimai/apdovanojimai_256/p40.html |archivedate=19 April 2014}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Luxembourg}}: Knight of the [[Order of the Gold Lion of the House of Nassau]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theroyalforums.com/forums/attachment.php?attachmentid=22949&d=1066680949 |title=Photographic image |website=Theroyalforums.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Mexico}}: Collar of the [[Order of the Aztec Eagle]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref name=Mexico>{{cite web| title=ACUERDO por el que se otorga a Su Majestad Margrethe II Reina de Dinamarca, la Condecoraci\u00f3n de la Orden 