}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://c7.alamy.com/comp/CR567K/margaret-ii-1641940-queen-of-denmark-since-1411972-with-husband-prince-CR567K.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=C7.alamy.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://c7.alamy.com/comp/CR566H/margaret-ii-1641940-queen-of-denmark-since-1411972-with-husband-prince-CR566H.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=C7.alamy.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://c7.alamy.com/comp/CR567M/margaret-ii-1641940-queen-of-denmark-since-1411972-with-husband-prince-CR567M.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=C7.alamy.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Romania}}: Collar of the [[Order of the Star of Romania]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/25/b4/1d/25b41d12a1ec59e8852fb8a0539d7d61.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=S-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Saudi Arabia}}: [[Order of Abdulaziz al Saud|The Collar of Abdulaziz Al Saud]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Slovakia}}: Grand Cross of the [[Order of the White Double Cross]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref name=Slovakia>{{cite web|url=http://kongehuset.dk/materialemappe/gallerier/2012/oktober-december/statsbesog-fra-slovakiet/statsbesog-fra-slovakiet-16.img |title=Photo of the Danish Royal couple with the Slovakian Presidential couple |website=Kongehuset.dk |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604092110/http://kongehuset.dk/materialemappe/gallerier/2012/oktober-december/statsbesog-fra-slovakiet/statsbesog-fra-slovakiet-16.img |archivedate=4 June 2014}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Slovenia}}: Member 1st Class of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Slovenia#Orders of Freedom of the Republic of Slovenia|Order of Freedom of the Republic of Slovenia]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Spain}}: 1,