orative Medals|50th Birthday Badge Medal of King Carl XVI Gustaf]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gettyimages.ca/detail/news-photo/50th-anniversary-of-king-carl-gustav-of-sweden-in-stockholm-news-photo/115116372|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417174053/http://www.gettyimages.ca/detail/news-photo/50th-anniversary-of-king-carl-gustav-of-sweden-in-stockholm-news-photo/115116372|url-status=dead|title=50th anniversary of king Carl Gustav of Sweden in Stockholm, Sweden...|archivedate=17 April 2015|website=Getty Images}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Sweden}}: Recipient of the [[Royal Jubilee Commemorative Medals|Ruby Jubilee Badge Medal of King Carl XVI Gustaf]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.corbisimages.com/stock-photo/rights-managed/42-51419189/king-carl-gustafs-40th-jubilee?popup%3D1 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=29 January 2017 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302001657/http://www.corbisimages.com/stock-photo/rights-managed/42-51419189/king-carl-gustafs-40th-jubilee?popup=1 |archivedate=2 March 2016}}</ref>\n* {{flag|South Africa}}: Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of Good Hope]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cover.dk/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/1999.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=Cover.dk |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|South Korea}}: Grand Cross with Chain of the [[Grand Order of Mugunghwa]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://c7.alamy.com/comp/DAKY35/danish-queen-margrethe-is-pictured-at-a-state-banquet-initiated-in-DAKY35.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=C7.alamy.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://c7.alamy.com/comp/DAKY3D/members-of-the-danish-royal-family-are-pictured-at-a-state-banquet-DAKY3D.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=C7.alamy.com |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref><ref name=SK>{{cite web| title=D\u00eener de gala au Palais de Fredensborg| url=http://www.noblesseetroyautes.com/nr01/2011/05/diner-de-gala-au-palais-de-fredensborg/| trans-title=Gala dinner at Fredensborg Palace| publisher=Noblesse et Royautes| date=13 May 2011| accessdate=11 December 2014| url-status=dead| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305040347/http://www.noblesseetroyautes.com/nr01/2011/05/diner-de-gala-au-palais-de-fredensborg/| archivedate=5 March 2016| df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Thailand}}: Knight of the [[Order of the Rajamitrabhorn]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gettyimages.co.uk/detail/news-photo/king-bhumibol-of-thailand-queen-margrethe-and-prince-henrik-news-photo/158069412|title=Queen Margrethe II of Denmark|author=Julian Parker|work=Getty Images|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://b.bimg.dk/node-images/162/620x411-c/162604-dronningen-giver-pengene-syv-gange-igen--.jpg |format=JPG |title=Photographic image |website=B.bimg.dk |accessdate=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Thailand}}: Knight of the [[Order of the Royal House of Chakri]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|United Arab Emirates}}: Grand Cordon of the [http://medals.org.uk/abu-dhabi/abu-dhabi001.htm Order of Al Kamal]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|United Kingdom}}: Stranger Lady of the [[Order of the Garter]] (7th Lady since 1901; 1979)<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://live-imagecollect.s3.amazonaws.com/preview/560/7d55e5ea4b50481 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=19 February 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308134555/http://live-imagecollect.s3.amazonaws.com/preview/560/7d55e5ea4b50481 |archivedate=8 March 2016}}</ref>\n* {{flag|United Kingdom}}: Recipient of the [[Royal Victorian Chain]] (1974)<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gettyimages.co.uk/detail/news-photo/queen-margrethe-of-denmark-and-queen-elizabeth-ii-of-great-news-photo/568919667|title=Gallery|author=Keystone|work=Getty Images|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Yugoslavia}}: Great Star of the [[Order of the Yugoslav Star]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n\n<gallery class=\"center\">\nFile:Royal_coat_of_arms_of_Denmark.svg|Royal coat of arms\nFile:Royal Standard of Denmark.svg|Royal standard\nFile:Royal Monogram of Queen Margrethe II of Denmark.svg|Royal monogram of Margrethe II\nFile:Private Monogram of Queen Margrethe of Denmark.svg|Personal monogram of Margrethe II\nFile:Dual Cypher of Margrethe and Henrik of Denmark.svg|Dual monogram of Margrethe II and husband Henrik, Prince Consort\n</gallery>\n\n==Ancestry==\n{{BLP unsourced section|date=April 2018}}\n{{see also|Family tree of the Danish royal family}}\n{{ahnentafel\n|collapsed=yes |align=center\n|boxstyle_1=background-color: #fcc;\n|boxstyle_2=background-color: #fb9;\n|boxstyle_3=background-color: #ffc;\n|boxstyle_4=background-color: #bfc;\n|1= 1. '''Margrethe II of Denmark'''\n|2= 2. [[Frederik IX of Denmark]]\n|3= 3. [[Ingrid of Sweden]]\n|4= 4. [[Christian X of Denmark]]\n|5= 5. [[Alexandrine of Mecklenburg-Schwerin]]\n|6= 6. [[Gustaf VI Adolf of Sweden]]\n|7= 7. [[Princess Margaret of Connaught]]\n|8= 8. [[Frederik VIII of Denmark]]\n|9= 9. [[Louise of Sweden|Princess Louise of Sweden]]\n|10= 10. [[Frederick Francis III, Grand Duke of Mecklenburg|Frederick Francis III, Grand Duke of Mecklenburg-Schwerin]]\n|11= 11. [[Grand Duchess Anastasia Mikhailovna of Russia]]\n|12= 12. [[Gustav V of Sweden]]\n|13= 13. [[Victoria of Baden]]\n|14= 14. [[Prince Arthur, Duke of Connaught and Strathearn]]\n|15= 15. [[Princess Louise Margaret of Prussia]]\n}}\n\n===Patrilineal descent===\n{{chart top|text-align=left|Patrilineal descent}}\n\n# [[Elimar I, Count of Oldenburg|Egilmar I of Lerigau]], dates unknown\n# [[Elimar II, Count of Oldenburg|Egilmar II of Lerigau]], d. 1142\n# [[Christian I, Count of Oldenburg]], d. 1167\n# [